<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-428] need to update leaderAndISR path in ZK conditionally in ReplicaManager</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-428</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When the leader tries to update the leaderAndISR path in ZK, the path may have been updated by the controller. When this happens, the leader should abort the update and log it. The controller should send new requests to the leader later on.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
